name: Bait Master - Passive Fish Generation
description:
This mod reintroduces passive fish generation.

I don't actually know what the original tick rate was, so I settled on the same rate the beehives use which is 1 fish every 120 seconds. Passive generation is based on the "insects" spawn weight, so you'll mostly get unappetizing fish.
changeNote: Added support for Shellfish Traps and Improved Shellfish Traps.
author: Exciderenox
